Besides our competitive teams, NUS Climbing also has a recreational arm catered for all who has an interest in the sport regardless of experience or background. The club trains on Tuesdays and Fridays 4 to 10pm at the USC Wall. Relax and unwind with a like-minded group of friends while keeping fit together!
