We also strongly believe in giving back and make effort to plan community-building events such as ClimbNUS and Boulderactive. Our teams have also done other community service projects like teaching climbing to underprivileged children with autism from Hope for the Journey Support Group.
&nbsp;
For more of what we do as NUS Climbing, check out our Instagram and Facebook page or drop any of the exco members a message.

