NUS Water Polo.info:
Description: NUS Water Polo comprises of both a men's and women's team. We participate in several competitions on a yearly basis, with the men's team being the reigning champions and women's team being first runners-up in the recent Singapore University Games 2019. Contact us if you are interested!
Find us on Instagram @nuswaterpolo
&nbsp;
Main Competitions: Water Polo main competitions are the Singapore University Games (SUniG), Institute Varsity Polytechnic (IVP) Games and the NUS open. The team also travels to Hong Kong on an annual basis to compete with teams from other countries on an international stage.
&nbsp;
